title: VA-Dance W Lance V3 D10-Chingame-08-HQMP3-DJKonabuzz
description:
DJ KonaBuzz (c) presents:
Dance With Lance (C) Version 3.0 Disk 10 Chingame
High Quality MP3 files from beatmixed DJ set
CD Quality WAV versions at http://djkonabuzz.blogspot.com
Electro/House Vibe tho some trax are from the pop scene; Many mashups/remixes. Hope you enjoy these.  The genderbend remix was a special mix done for my live audience, and the inspiration for the disk title.  I really like the flow between tracks 7, 8, 9, 10.

Note:  I am changing the location of CD quality .WAV files to my blog in order to save some disk space and bandwidth on this end.  WAV files are now posted for direct (not torrent) download at http://djkonabuzz.blogspot.com
